{"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI12ViewModifierP"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSToolBarTop"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"toolBarTop(_:hasLargeTitle:subtitle:leadingItems:trailingItems:)"},{"type":"text","text":"  View helper applies a SwiftUI toolbar configuration."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Appearances","text":"Appearances"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"With Liquid Glass \/ iOS 26+ the OS will change the rendering of the toolbar items depending to the context:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The OS can group the items of same types in one group with kind of rectangle (e.g. views with menus)","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"But for buttons items they will remain isolated","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The placement of the title can be leading or centered depending to the length of the text","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The text can be truncated if there is not enough remaining space","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The OS can apply another style for the back button","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Without Liquid Glass \/ iOS 18 and lower, the OS won’t change that much the style of the toolbar items, Items won’t be visually grouped."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Globaly the appearence of the * navigation bar* elements is changed by the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oudsNavigationBarAppearance"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"helper of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" that must be applyed on the root view of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NavigationStack"},{"type":"text","text":" for example."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Technical-constraints","text":"Technical constraints"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To be sure for iOS 18 and lower the back buttton and text have the good color, in your main view apply the following accent color:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    struct AppMainView: View {","        var body: some View {","            ContentView()","                .accentColor(theme.colors.contentDefault)","        }","    }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Platform-considerations","text":"Platform considerations"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component is available on iOS, iPadOS, and visionOS","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component is not available for watchOS, tvOS and macOS","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Badges-uses","text":"Badges uses"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For iOS 26 with Liquid Glass, the system badge is used because the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" does not provide a suitable rendering with the glassified effect applied on the top toolbar."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS until 18 and without Liquid Glass "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBadge","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is always used."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Code-sample","text":"Code sample"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    ContentView()","        .toolBarTop(\"Title\",","            leadingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(navigation: .back())","            },","            trailingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(label: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","                OUDSToolBarItem(icon: Image(decorative: \"some_image\"), accessibilityLabel: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","            }","        )"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-ios-tool-bar-top","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Liquid-Glass","text":"Liquid Glass"},{"type":"heading","level":4,"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_Orange_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_Orange_dark"}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_OrangeCompact_dark"}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_LiquidGlass_Sosh_light"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"image","identifier":"component_toolBarTop_Liqui